data.description: Welcome to Henry County, Georgia, Located in the City of Stockbridge, just minutes away from the exclusive Eagles Landing Country Club you will find this early 2000's home. This 2-bed 2-bath home Spanish roof ranch style home is perfect for the retiree, if you are down sizing, or an investor looking for passive income. Situated near local Hospitals, shopping and attractions it is an ideal location for someone relocating from another state, country or area that would like to be close to all amenities. Downtown Atlanta is just a short drive away with I-75 being just down the street. Come see this gem today!!
